<CENTER><STRONG><FONT  SIZE=+2><FONT SIZE=+3>P</FONT>artnership for <FONT SIZE=+3>D</FONT>istributed <FONT SIZE=+3>L</FONT>earning </FONT> </STRONG> </CENTER>
