Twigg, Carol A. "Navigating the Transition." <EM>Educom Review</EM> 29, no. 6 (November/December 1994): 21-24. (Part 3 of 3-part article.) Available online at URL <A HREF="http://www.educom.edu/educom.review/review.94/nov.dec/twigg">http://www.educom.edu/educom.review/review.94/nov.dec/twigg</A>.
<P>
Combined text of the three parts is also available online at URL <A HREF="http://www.educom.edu/program/nlii/keydocs/monograph.html">http://www.educom.edu/program/nlii/keydocs/monograph.html</A>.
<P>
<LI><STRONG>Douglas Van Houweling</STRONG><BR>
Van Houweling, Douglas E. "The National Network: A National Interest." <EM>Educom Review</EM> 24, no. 2 (Summer 1989): 14-18.
</UL>
