<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFCE7" TEXT="#00006F">
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><STRONG>From Reality to Virtuality:<BR> Readings and Resources in Virtual Reality</FONT></STRONG>
<P>
Compiled by: Carolyn Kotlas, MSLS<BR>
Institute for Academic Technology<BR>
Last revised: June 22, 1996
<P>
Prepared for the IAT Satellite Broadcast<BR>
<EM>From Reality to Virtuality: New Tools for Distributed Learning</EM><BR>
Presented on March 21, 1996
</CENTER>
<P>
<A HREF="#papers">Papers and Articles</A><BR>
<A HREF="#books">Books</A><BR>
<A HREF="#www">WWW Resources (Guides, Overviews and Bibliographies) </A><BR>
<A HREF="#journals">Journals with Virtual Reality Coverage</A> <BR>
