	Telecommunications</EM>.
<P>
<EM>EIA/TIA-569: Commercial Building Standard for the Telecommunications
	Pathways and Spaces</EM>, October 1992.
<P>
<EM>EIA/TIA-568: Commercial Building Telecommunications Wiring Standard</EM>,
	July 1991.
<P>
<EM>CSA T528: Design Guidelines for Administration of Telecommunications in
	Commercial Buildings</EM>.
<P>
<EM>CSA T529: Design Guidelines for Telecommunications Wiring Systems in
	Commercial Buildings</EM>.
<P>
<EM>TSB-53: Extended Specifications for 150-Ohm Shielded Twisted Pair Cable
	and Connectors</EM>, Forthcoming.
<P>
<EM>CSA T527: Grounding and Bonding Requirements for Telecommunications in
	Commercial Buildings</EM>.
<P>
<EM>EIA/TIA PN-2347: Grounding and Bonding Requirements for
	Telecommunications in Commercial Buildings</EM>, Forthcoming.
<P>
