<A NAME="11"></A><STRONG>INFOBITS FTP ARCHIVE DISCONTINUED</STRONG><P>

In an effort to minimize the number of computers where we keep back
issues of <EM>Infobits</EM>, we discontinued the archive on our anonymous FTP
site this month. Back issues of Infobits in plain text format as they
were originally emailed are now available on our Web site at
<A HREF="http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/text/index.html">http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/text/index.html</A>
