<P>
A combined subject listing of the IAT Library's Information Resource Guides series and the "Librarian's Links" documents is now available at URL <A HREF="http://www.iat.unc.edu/guides/subjects.html">http://www.iat.unc.edu/guides/subjects.html</A>
