<A NAME="9"></A><STRONG>IAT INFOBITS IN HTML FORMAT</STRONG><P>

All back issues of <EM>IAT Infobits</EM> have now been converted to HTML format
and are available at URL <A HREF="http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/infobits.html">http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/infobits.html</A>
<P>
The conversion process is more than a cosmetic change. URLs included in
an article were checked and, if necessary, updated. Hyperlinks were
made for the URLs. Some articles were also revised or deleted
altogether because services mentioned had been discontinued. Readers
can still retrieve unchanged copies of Infobits issues as they were
originally distributed at URL
<A HREF="http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/text/index.html">http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/text/index.html</A>
