<A NAME="2"></A><STRONG>NEWJOUR LISTSERV</STRONG><P>

NewJour is a listserv that announces new electronic journals. The
traffic on this list has grown so much that NewJour, in an effort to
reduce the number of messages subscribers receive, is now available in
digest form. To receive one daily listing of new electronic journals,
send email to: <A HREF="mailto:mjd@ccat.sas.upenn.edu">mjd@ccat.sas.upenn.edu</A> 
with the following message:
<P>
<SAMP>subscribe newjour-digest</SAMP>
<P>
Do <I>not</I> put anything in the email subject line. 
<BR>
Do <I>not</I> include your name or any other information in the message.
<P>
