<A HREF="http://www.peacewire.org/pw/harticles.html">http://www.peacewire.org/pw/harticles.html</A> and the Hiroshima-Nagasaki
Project at URL <A HREF="http://www.peacewire.org/pw/hiromenu.html">http://www.peacewire.org/pw/hiromenu.html</A>
