<A NAME="3"></A><STRONG>WAIT TILL THE MIDNIGHT HOUR</STRONG><P>

Project Gutenberg has added the following works to its electronic text
collection just in time for your online Halloween reading pleasure:
<P>
<EM>Charlotte Temple</EM>, by Susanna Rowson   -- filename: chtem10.xxx<BR>
