<P>
Carnegie Mellon Lycos searcher:<BR>
<A HREF="http://lycos.cs.cmu.edu/">http://lycos.cs.cmu.edu/</A>
<P>
EINet Galaxy:<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.einet.net/galaxy.html">http://www.einet.net/galaxy.html</A>
<P>
