with the message:<BR>
<SAMP>LIBSEARCH CNC93</SAMP><BR>
Papers can be read online on the CAUSE Gopher server at URL <A HREF="gopher://cause-gopher.Colorado.EDU:70/11/conferences/CAUSE93">gopher://cause-gopher.Colorado.EDU:70/11/conferences/CAUSE93</A>
