Note that the graphics are available in 2-3 different formats: 150 or
300 dpi, and Postscript.  You will have some choices to make and will
be importing the different pieces one by one. There is also an ftp (not
gopher) file that is quite large and contains all the chapters in one
file...as ASCII text files.
