<LI>Erv Blythe (Virginia Tech)
<LI>Keng Chua (Southern Cross University - Australia)
<LI>Roger Debreceny (Southern Cross University - Australia)
<LI>David Greenbaum (University of California - Berkeley)
<LI>Clair Goldsmith (University of Texas at Austin)
<LI>Rodney Hersberger (California State University, Bakersfield)
