<P>
<A NAME="bugs"></A><STRONG><EM>Entomology</EM></STRONG>
<P>
<STRONG>Drosophila</STRONG><BR>
<A HREF="http://www-leland.stanford.edu/~ger/drosophila.html">http://www-leland.stanford.edu/~ger/drosophila.html</A>
<P>
<STRONG>FlyBase</STRONG> -- Drosophila genome database<BR>
<A HREF="gopher://flybase.bio.indiana.edu:82/h">gopher://flybase.bio.indiana.edu:82/h</A>
<P>
<STRONG>Flybrain</STRONG> -- an online atlas and database of the Drosophila nervous system<BR>
<A HREF="http://flybrain.uni-freiburg.de/">http://flybrain.uni-freiburg.de/</A>
<P>
<STRONG>Entomology</STRONG> -- Colorado State University<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.colostate.edu/Depts/Entomology/ent.html">http://www.colostate.edu/Depts/Entomology/ent.html</A>
<P>
<EM>Search for more on entomology...</EM><BR>
