<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Selected Web Sites in the Humanities</TITLE>
<!-- Created Spring 1995 by Donna Cornick & Thomas Nixon -->
<!-- Last revised: August 18. 1995 by Carolyn Kotlas -->
<!-- Filename = irg-25.html -->
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFCE7" TEXT="#00006F">
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><STRONG>Selected Web Sites in the Humanities
</FONT></STRONG>
<P>
Compiled by:
Donna Cornick,<BR>
Electronic Reference Services Librarian, Davis Library, UNC-Chapel Hill<BR>
and Thomas Nixon, <BR>
Reference Librarian, Davis Library, UNC-Chapel Hill<BR>
for the Spring 1995 Conference (March 6, 1995)<BR>
