SRI International. <I>Study of Communications Technology in Higher Education</I>. Washington: The Corporation for Public Broadcasting, 1994.<BR>
For free copy write to Publications Coordinator, CPB, 901 E Street, NW, Washington, DC 20004 or fax to 202-783-1019 or send email to Ric Schooley, <A HREF="mailto:rschooley@cpb.org">rschooley@cpb.org</A>
<P>
