<STRONG><EM>Online/Electronic Media Resources</EM></STRONG>
<P>
Note: The following online resources represent only a broad survey of
the many information services that are available. You should be aware
that these include commercial (fee based) services, 800# and long
distance direct dial services, as  well as Internet accessible (gopher,
listserve, telnet, etc.) information. Before subscribing to any
fee-based services and/or logging on to long distance connects for
extended periods, we suggest that you contact the information providers
to insure that the information is relevant and useful for your
purposes.
