<BR>
Cost ranges from about 10 cents for a simple abstract to hundreds of dollars for proprietary financial information.  Fees are charged to a user's credit card.
<LI><STRONG>Symantec's Internet FastFind:</STRONG> <A HREF="http://www.symantec.com/iff/">http://www.symantec.com/iff/</A>
<BR>
Workstation-based meta-search engine. Similar to Metacrawler with added features.  Cost: US $49.95. 30-day trial version available.
<P>
</UL>
