<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><STRONG>Higher Education/K-12 Connection: Bibliography
</FONT></STRONG>
<P>
Compiled by Carolyn Kotlas, MSLS<BR>
Institute for Academic Technology<BR>
Last revised: August 18, 1995
