<HEAD>
<TITLE>Bibliography Formatting Software: Bibliography</TITLE>
<!-- Converted to HTML format: August 1995 -->
<!-- Last revised: August 19, 1996 by Carolyn Kotlas -->
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFCE7" TEXT="#00006F">
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><STRONG>Bibliography Formatting Software: Bibliography</FONT></STRONG>
<P>
Compiled by Carolyn Kotlas, MSLS<BR>
Institute for Academic Technology<BR>
Last revised: August 19, 1996</CENTER>
<P>

The document, <EM>Bibliography Formatting Software</EM>, written by Sue Stigleman
and published by the Institute for Academic Technology, has been out of
print since 1994, and no copies are available. Due to the complicated
charts in the hardcopy version, no electronic version was ever
available on our FTP or Web site.
<P>
Although this document is no longer available and Sue has no immediate
plans to revise it, she continues to write articles on the subject of
bibliography formatting software. Below are citations to articles she
has written on this topic.
<P>
Stigleman, Sue. "Bibliography Formatting Software:  A Buying Guide."
	<EM>Database</EM> 15 (February 1992): 15-27.
<P>
Stigleman, Sue. "Bibliography Formatting Software:  An Update."
	<EM>Database</EM> 16 (February 1993): 24-37.
<P>
Stigleman, Sue. "Bibliography Formatting Software:  An Updated Buying
	Guide for 1994." <EM>Database</EM> 17 (December 1994): 53-65.
<P>
<IMG SRC="../media/gifs/new.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=13 BORDER=0> Stigleman, Sue. "Bibliography Programs Do Windows." 
	<EM>Database </EM> 19 (April/May 1996): 57-60, 62-66.
<P>
Stigleman, Sue. "EndNote Plus:  Macintosh Bibliography Power On A PC."
	<EM>Database 15</EM> (October 1992): 50-55
<P>
Stigleman, Sue. "IdeaList:  Flexible Text Storage And Retrieval
	Software."  <EM>Database</EM> 15 (June 1992): 50-56
<P>
Stigleman, Sue. "Papyrus:  Good Bibliographic Value at a Reasonable
	Price." <EM>Database 16</EM> (June 1993): 82-87.
<P>
You can contact Sue at:
<P><UL>
Sue Stigleman<BR>
Education Services Librarian<BR>
Information and Media Services<BR>
Mountain Area Health Education Center (MAHEC)<BR>
501 Biltmore Avenue<BR>
Asheville, NC  28801-4686<BR>
tel:  (704) 257-4452<BR>
fax:  (704) 258-2099<BR>
email:  <A HREF="mailto://sues@shamu.mtn.ncahec.org">sues@shamu.mtn.ncahec.org</A>
</UL>
<P>
