<STRONG>URL</STRONG>: <A HREF="http://www.iat.unc.edu/guides/irg-16.html">http://www.iat.unc.edu/guides/irg-16.html</A><BR>
© <A HREF="../general/copyright.html">Copyright</A> 1994, 1996 Institute for Academic Technology. All rights reserved.
</FONT>
