<P>
Last revised: February 7, 1997
<BR>

<P>A list of journals, magazines, and newsletters in the Institute for Academic Technology Library covering  educational technology, multimedia development, computers and computer programming, the Internet, and related topics. Links are also included to newspapers and other publications that are not in the Library, but can be accessed on the World Wide Web.
<HR>
<UL>
Note: <BR>
<U>Underlined</U> titles <EM>also</EM> have pages on the World Wide Web. <BR>
Titles with the "<FONT SIZE="-2">WEB</FONT>" notation are <EM>only</EM> available on the Web. <BR>
<A NAME="*">
Titles with the "<FONT SIZE="-2">CD-ROM</FONT>" notation are available in the IAT Library <EM>only</EM> on the <EM>Computer Select</EM> CD-ROM.</A> 
</UL>
