<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" width="100%"
units="RELATIVE" colspec="L75 C5 C20">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" valign="top">Welcome to the online
        presence for <i>The Knoxville News-Sentinel</i>! We're
        glad you've chosen to stop by. Since you're here, we
        assume you need assistance using this site or want to
        know where to find something. <p><strong>Quick Tip:</strong>
        We change our content often. If you hit a page that seems
        to have outdated news, try reloading. In Netscape, click
        on the &quot;Reload&quot; button; in Microsoft Internet
        Explorer, click on the &quot;Refresh&quot; button.</p>
        <p>If you ever have questions or otherwise need to
        contact <i>The News-Sentinel</i> staff, check out our <a
        href="reachus.html">contact page</a>. It includes
        telephone numbers and e-mail addresses for our staff. </p>
        <p>Add our top page to your list of <strong>bookmarks</strong>
        or <strong>favorites</strong>. Here's how: <a
        href="/help/bookmark.html">Bookmarks</a> </p>
        <p>Having trouble finding what you're looking for on the
        Internet? Try our <a href="links/findit.html">Find It</a>
        page.</p>
        <p>Having trouble finding back information on our site?
        See our <a href="links/yesterday-news.html">Yesterday's
        News</a> page.</p>
        <p><a href="http://browserwatch.iworld.com/plug-in.html"><img
        src="images/icons/bw-pp-new.gif" border="0" hspace="5"
        vspace="5" width="88" height="31"></a></p>
        <p>Need a <strong>browser plugin</strong> for ShockWave,
        QuickTime, MIDI and more? Check the <a
        href="http://browserwatch.iworld.com/plug-in.html">BrowserWatch
        Plug-In Plaza</a></p>
        <p><img src="images/v3/promos/knoxnewscomlogo150.gif"
        alt="ads/knoxnews/" width="150" height="26"></p>
        <p>Knoxnews.com <a href="ads/knoxnews/index.html">pricing</a>,
        <a href="http://www.infi.net/support/">technical support</a>,<a
        href="http://www.infi.net/411.html"> InfiNet 411</a>.</p>
        </td>
        <td align="center">&nbsp;<br>
        </td>
        <td align="center" valign="top" width="185"
        bgcolor="#99C6FF"><b>This site best viewed with:</b> <a
