<title>Advertising on the Web Information</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<p align="center"><img src="../images/logos/logo.gif"
alt="Knoxville News-Sentinel Online Publishing" width="399"
height="153"> </p>

<h1 align="center">Advertise On The Web</h1>

<p><a href="/"><font size="5" face="Brush Script MT"><b><img
src="../images/logos/KNOX-LINK-US.GIF" alt="knoxnews.com"
align="right" border="0" hspace="7" vspace="7" width="151"
height="53"></b></font></a><font size="5" face="Brush Script MT"><b>T</b></font>he
Knoxville News-Sentinel offers advertisers a variety of ways to
establish an Internet presence that suits their specific budget
and business needs. The News-Sentinel&#146;s web sites are the
most popular in the East Tennessee region. The <a
href="http://www.knoxnews.com">Knoxnews.com</a> site receives
over a quarter of a million visits each month from users seeking
information on the Knoxville area, Tennessee sports, area jobs, homes,
the latest movie reviews, restaurants, local entertainment,
vacation destinations or just to read the interesting stories
written by the Sentinel&#146;s talented staff. <a
href="http://www.knoxnews.com">Knoxnews.com</a> is the one stop Internet resource
for information about Knoxville and East Tennessee.</p>

<p>&nbsp;<font size="5" face="Brush Script MT"><b>T</b></font>he<u> </u><a
href="http://www.govols.com">GoVols.com</a> site is the number
one Web site for University of Tennessee sports. <a
href="http://www.govols.com">GoVols.com</a> is receiving half a million
visits each month from Vol fans seeking the latest UT sporting
news, color action photos of the Vols in action and to
participate in the many Vol forums. Fans can also listen to UT
games on the Internet and keep up with the Heisman Trophy race. <a
href="http://www.govols.com">GoVols.com</a> is <b><i>UT Sports!</i></b></p>

<p><font size="5" face="Brush Script MT"><b>A</b></font>dvertisers
have several areas from which to choose. A <a
href="../merchants">Merchant&#146;s Index</a> is now
available to area businesses that categorize companies by
business type and location. These &quot;Unenhanced&quot; listings include
the company&#146;s name, address and phone number, and are free
to businesses that request the service. The listings can also be
&quot;enhanced&quot; with hyperlinked text or a linked graphic. Banner
ads, sponsorships and web development are also available. The
Knoxville News-Sentinel has a full-time Internet staff that can
design, maintain and market a web presence to meet your company specifications. </p>

<p><font size="5" face="Brush Script MT"><b>T</b></font>o become
a part of the number one Internet resource of what&#146;s
happening in Knoxville and East Tennessee contact The Knoxville
News-Sentinel&#146;s Online Publishing department at <font
face="Arial Rounded MT Bold">(423) 971-3473</font>, or e-mail us
at <a href="mailto:kelsey@knoxnews.com"><font
face="Arial Rounded MT Bold">kelsey@knoxnews.com</font></a></p>

<p><font size="2">&nbsp;</font></p>
<div align="center"><center>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="80%">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" width="20%"><a href="merchants.html"><font
        size="2"><b>The Merchant&#146;s Index</b></font></a></td>
        <td align="center" width="20%"><a href="busilinks.htm"><font
        size="2"><b>Business Links Page </b></font></a></td>
        <td align="center" width="20%"><a href="banner.htm"><font
        size="2"><b>Banners </b></font></a></td>
        <td align="center" width="20%"><a href="newban.htm"><font
