        size="2"><b>GENERAL EXPO INFORMATION</b></font><p><font
        size="2"><b>Show Dates &amp; Hours</b></font></p>
        <p><font color="#732B66" size="2">Friday, April 4, 1997</font><font
        size="2"><br>
        10 a.m. - 6 p.m.<br>
        </font><font color="#732B66" size="2">Saturday, April 5,
        1997</font><font size="2"><br>
        10 a.m. - 6 p.m.<br>
        </font><font color="#732B66" size="2">Sunday, April 6,
        1997</font><font size="2"><br>
        Noon - 5 p.m.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2">All booths must be manned during show
        hours.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Location</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Knoxville Convention/Exhibition Center<br>
        525 Henley Street<br>
        Knoxville, Tennessee 37902<br>
        (423) 544-5371</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Move-In</b></font></p>
        <p><font color="#732B66" size="2">Thursday, April 3 </font><font
        size="2"><br>
        9 a.m. - 9 p.m.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Move-Out</b></font></p>
        <p><font color="#732B66" size="2">Sunday, April 6 </font><font
        size="2"><br>
        5 p.m. - 9 p.m.<br>
        Booths may not be broken down before 5 p.m. Sunday.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Security</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Security begins at 9 a.m. on Thursday,
        April 3, continuing around the clock until 9 p.m. on
        Sunday, April 6.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Sales Tax</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">8 3 % must be collected on all sales.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b><br>
        Public Admission</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Adults $5.00</font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Youth 6 - 12 $3.00</font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Under 6 Free</font></p>
        <p><font color="#732B66" size="2">$1.00 off with
        News-Sentinel Advantage Card.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Each exhibitor will receive 100 tickets
        per booth purchased to distribute to customers and
        friends at no additional cost plus the opportunity to
        purchase additional tickets at $1.00 each.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Advertising &amp; Promotion</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">We recognize the importance of
        aggressive, well-planned and implemented marketing
        programs to ensure a successful show for you as an
        exhibitor. Our results-generating program utilizes a
        multimedia approach, guaranteed to deliver the high
        quality audience you want to see. Our promotion program
        is valued at over $250,000 and some of the marketing
        tactics will include:</font></p>
        <ul>
            <li><font size="2">Promotional ads in The
                News-Sentinel</font> </li>
            <li><font size="2">Women Today Expo section inserted
                in <br>
                The News-Sentinel</font> </li>
            <li><font size="2">Media buys on local television
                stations</font> </li>
            <li><font size="2">Media buys and ticket giveaway
                promotions with radio stations</font> </li>
            <li><font size="2">Extensive outdoor campaign week of
                expo</font> </li>
            <li><font size="2">Point of purchase displays at
                exhibitors businesses</font> </li>
            <li><font size="2">Complimentary tickets distributed
                by exhibitors</font> </li>
        </ul>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Official Exposition Program</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">Produced by The News-Sentinel and
        distributed to over 282,500 adults on Wednesday, April 2,
        1997. The Women Today Expo program features the
        celebrities, exhibitors and schedules for workshops,
        seminars, cooking school and entertainment stages. Every
        exhibitor receives an ad in the section. Ad price is
        included in package price; size of ad determined by the
        package purchased.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2"><b>Exposition Sponsors</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">The News-Sentinel<br>
        Scripps Howard Cable<br>
        WBIR-TV, Channel 10</font></p>
        </td>
        <td valign="top" width="25%" bgcolor="#BDD9EE"><font
        size="2"><b>Exhibitor Rate Information</b></font><p><font
        size="2"><b>Package A</b></font></p>
        <p><font size="2">10' x 10' booth<br>
        1/8 page ad in section<br>
