        src="jh/pauldive.jpg"
        alt="SEC Swimming and Diving Championships" align="right"
        hspace="0" width="411" height="315" naturalsizeflag="0"></td>
        <td><font size="2" face="Arial,Helvetica,Frutiger">Against
        a background of colored glass windows, springboard divers
        Courtney Roberts of LSU and Cari-Ann Hayer of Auburn warm
        up for the three meter diving competion during the SEC
        Swimning and Diving Championships at the UT Aquatics
        Center in March 1996. <br>
        <b><i>Photo by Paul Efrid.</i></b></font></td>
