</p>
<p align=left><font size=5><b>Tell Us Your Smoky Mountain Vacation Stories ...</b></font></p>
<p align=right><font size=4><b><i>... And You Might Win A Free T-Shirt</i></b></font></p>
<p>Did a bear visit your campsite? Did you have a close encounter with chiggers? Dad drove off the 
edge of the road? Just how many deer did you see in Cades Cove? You never made it past the 
Pigeon Forge outlet malls? Tell us your vacation tales from the Smokies and you might win a 100 
percent cotton, long sleeve, crew neck T-shirt. </p>
<p>We'll be giving a T-shirt away every Friday and we'll post the winner right here. The Dec. 30, 1996, 
winner is <b>Richard Enix
<b>of <b>Lake City, TN</b>. Congratulations, Richard! </p>
<p>Just fill out the form below to enter and give us your best vacation tale from the Smokies. </p>
<p>We'll post the best tales on the Web and you'll be famous. </p>
<hr size=5>
<h1 align=center>Vacation Tales from the Smokies</h1>
